                 encoding = "UTF-8", stringsAsFactors=FALSE)

base <- base %>% 
  rename(pk_customer = X.U.FEFF.pk_customer)


base <- base %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(pedidos = sum(purchase)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by ='pk_customer') %>% 
    mutate(pedidos2 = ifelse(pedidos == 0, 'Sem compra',
                           ifelse(pedidos == 1, 'Uma compra',
                                  ifelse(pedidos == 2, 'Duas compras',
                                         'Mais que duas compras'))))



base <- base %>% 
  filter(purchase > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_compra = min(visitas)) %>% 
  right_join(base, by = 'pk_customer')

base <- base %>% 
  mutate(is_weekly_campaign = ifelse(is_weekly_campaign <= -1,0,is_weekly_campaign),
         is_image_search = ifelse(is_image_search <= -1,0,is_image_search),
         is_fit_finder = ifelse(is_fit_finder <= -1,0,is_fit_finder)) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.numeric, replace_na, 0)
g_legend<-function(a.gplot){
  tmp <- ggplot_gtable(ggplot_build(a.gplot))
  leg <- which(sapply(tmp$grobs, function(x) x$name) == "guide-box")
  legend <- tmp$grobs[[leg]]
  return(legend)}

base <- base %>% 
  mutate(pedidos2 = factor(pedidos2, levels = c('Sem compra', 'Uma compra', 'Duas compras', 'Mais que duas compras')))

 base <- base %>% 
  mutate(is_weekly_campaign = ifelse(is_weekly_campaign > 0, 1, 0),
         is_image_search = ifelse(is_image_search > 0, 1, 0),

resumo <- base %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = max(is_weekly_campaign),
            is_image_search = max(is_image_search),
            is_fit_finder = max(is_fit_finder),
            is_dft_eco = max(is_dft_eco)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = sum(is_weekly_campaign),
            is_image_search = sum(is_image_search),
            is_fit_finder = sum(is_fit_finder),
            is_dft_eco = sum(is_dft_eco),
            clientes = n())

num_clientes <- as.integer(resumo %>% 
  select(clientes))


resumo2 <-base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(is_weekly_campaign = sum(is_weekly_campaign),
            prim_visita_WC = min(visitas)) %>% 
  full_join(base %>% 
              filter(is_image_search > 0) %>% 
              group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
              summarise(is_image_search = sum(is_image_search),
                        prim_visita_IS = min(visitas)),
            by = 'pk_customer')%>% 
  full_join(base %>% 
              filter(is_fit_finder > 0) %>% 
              group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
              summarise(is_fit_finder = sum(is_fit_finder),
                        prim_visita_FF = min(visitas)),
            by = 'pk_customer')%>% 
  full_join(base %>% 
              filter(is_dft_eco > 0) %>% 
              group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
              summarise(is_dft_eco = sum(is_dft_eco),
                        prim_visita_DE = min(visitas)),
            by = 'pk_customer')



resumo3 <- resumo2 %>% 
  filter(is_image_search > 0) %>%

freq <- base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_visitas = min(visitas),
            prim_date = min(id_date)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  mutate(flag_pos = ifelse(visitas < Prim_visitas, 0,1),
         prim_date = as.character(prim_date),
         prim_date = as.Date(prim_date,'%Y%m%d'),
         id_date = as.character(id_date),
         id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')
         ) %>% 
  filter(Prim_visitas >= 3,
         id_date >= prim_date - 30,
         id_date <= prim_date + 30
         )


freq <- freq %>% 
  filter(flag_pos == 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(max_date = max(id_date),
            min_date = min(id_date),
            visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
  mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
         diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
         diff_date = diff_date,
         freq_visita_mes_pre = visitas/30) %>% 
  select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pre) %>% 
  inner_join(
    freq %>% 
      filter(flag_pos == 1) %>% 
      group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
      summarise(max_date = max(Sys.Date()),
                min_date = min(id_date),
                visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
      mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
             diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
             diff_date = diff_date,
             freq_visita_mes_pos = visitas/30) %>% 
      select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pos),
    by = 'pk_customer'
    ) %>% 
  mutate(diff_freq_visita = freq_visita_mes_pos/freq_visita_mes_pre)


freq %>% 
  summarise(qtd_clientes = n(),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pre = median(freq_visita_mes_pre),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pos = median(freq_visita_mes_pos),
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = Mediana_freq_visita_pos/Mediana_freq_visita_pre - 1,
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = paste(round(Mediana_diff_freq_visita*100,2), '%', sep = '')
            ) %>% 
  mutate(Mediana_freq_visita_pre = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pre,2),
         Mediana_freq_visita_pos = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pos,2)) %>% 
  knitr::kable(caption = "Diferença na frequencia de visitas de clientes com campanhas semanais - 30 dias pré e pós utilização (só clientes com visita pré e pós)") %>%  
  kable_styling()

clientes <- base %>% 
  filter(is_weekly_campaign > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(prim_visitas = min(visitas)) %>% 
  right_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer,prim_visitas,Prim_compra,pedidos2) %>% 
  summarise(max_visitas = max(visitas)) %>% 
  mutate(flag = ifelse(prim_visitas <= Prim_compra | (Prim_compra == 0 & !is.na(prim_visitas)),
                       'Antes da Primeira compra','Sem Evento ou pós compra')) %>% 
  mutate_if(is.character, replace_na, 'Sem Evento ou pós compra')

         freq_visita_mes_pre = visitas/30) %>% 
  select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pre) %>% 
  left_join(
    freq %>% 
      filter(flag_pos == 1) %>% 
      group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
      summarise(max_date = max(Sys.Date()),
                min_date = min(id_date),
                visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
      mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
             diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
             diff_date = diff_date,
             freq_visita_mes_pos = visitas/30) %>% 
      select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pos),
    by = 'pk_customer'
    ) %>% 
  mutate(diff_freq_visita = freq_visita_mes_pos/freq_visita_mes_pre)


freq %>% 
  summarise(qtd_clientes = n(),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pre = median(freq_visita_mes_pre),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pos = median(freq_visita_mes_pos),
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = Mediana_freq_visita_pos/Mediana_freq_visita_pre - 1,
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = paste(round(Mediana_diff_freq_visita*100,2), '%', sep = '')
            ) %>% 
  mutate(Mediana_freq_visita_pre = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pre,2),
         Mediana_freq_visita_pos = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pos,2)) %>% 
  knitr::kable(caption = "Diferença na frequencia de visitas de clientes com Busca Look - 30 dias pré e pós utilização") %>%
  kable_styling()

freq <- base %>% 
  filter(is_dft_eco > 0) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(Prim_visitas = min(visitas)) %>% 
  inner_join(base, by = 'pk_customer') %>% 
  mutate(flag_pos = ifelse(visitas < Prim_visitas, 0,1)) %>% 
  filter(Prim_visitas >= 3)
  

freq <- freq %>% 
  filter(flag_pos == 0) %>% 
  mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
         id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
  group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
  summarise(max_date = max(id_date),
            min_date = min(id_date),
            visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
  mutate(diff_date = max_date-min_date,
         diff_date = as.integer(diff_date)+1,
         diff_date = diff_date/30,
         freq_visita_mes_pre = visitas/30) %>% 
  select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pre) %>% 
  inner_join(
    freq %>% 
      filter(flag_pos == 1) %>% 
      mutate(id_date = as.character(id_date),
             id_date = as.Date(id_date,'%Y%m%d')) %>% 
      group_by(pk_customer) %>% 
      summarise(max_date = max(Sys.Date()),
                min_date = min(id_date),
                visitas = length(unique(id_date))) %>% 
      mutate(freq_visita_mes_pos = visitas/30) %>% 
      select(pk_customer, freq_visita_mes_pos),
    by = 'pk_customer'
    ) %>% 
  mutate(diff_freq_visita = freq_visita_mes_pos/freq_visita_mes_pre)


freq %>% 
  summarise(qtd_clientes = n(),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pre = median(freq_visita_mes_pre),
            Mediana_freq_visita_pos = median(freq_visita_mes_pos),
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = Mediana_freq_visita_pos/Mediana_freq_visita_pre - 1,
            Mediana_diff_freq_visita = paste(round(Mediana_diff_freq_visita*100,2), '%', sep = '')
            ) %>% 
  mutate(Mediana_freq_visita_pre = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pre,2),
         Mediana_freq_visita_pos = round(Mediana_freq_visita_pos,2)) %>% 
  knitr::kable(caption = "Diferença na frequencia de visitas de clientes com Fit Finder") %>%  
  kable_styling()
